Q: how to instanciate the template repos?
A: clone template repos:
   # git clone TEMPL_URL REPOS_NAME
   # cd REPOS_NAME
   set origin to the destination repos:
   # git remote set-url origin DEST_URL
   first push:
   # git push -u origin master

Q: how to commit and push changes to the destination repository?
A: stage everything:
   # git add .
   commit:
   # git commit
   push to destination origin:
   # git push
